1
00:00:00,100 --> 00:00:02,876
Here is one useful thing to watch for.

2
00:00:02,826 --> 00:00:07,090
Pressing the power button many times does not make it faster.

3
00:00:07,090 --> 00:00:09,415
One press, then wait.

4
00:00:09,415 --> 00:00:14,035
If it happens, pause, reset, and try again calmly.

